            "text": "<p>Regular inspection of playground equipment is important, it is equally important to look for hazards on the playground property as a whole. <br\/><br\/>Look for the following <strong>&#8681; <\/strong> <strong>⇩ <\/strong> <strong>⇩<\/strong><\/p>",
