        "color_scheme": "scheme-3",
        "header": "",
        "heading_font_size": 16,
        "paragraph": "<p>If you detect safety hazards during your inspection, record, repair, and replace the equipment as quickly as possilbe to reduce the possibility of injury.<\/p>",
